Mysynthdata

Source: R/data.R
mysynthdata.Rd

Synthetic data set for Managing Churn to Maximize Profits

mysynthdata

Format

A data frame with 200 rows and 14 variables:

w

integer the treatment dummy

x1

integer covariate 1

x2

integer covariate 2

x3

integer covariate 3

x4

integer covariate 4

x5

integer covariate 5

x6

integer covariate 6

x7

integer covariate 7

x8

integer covariate 8

x9

integer covariate 9

x10

integer covariate 10

x11

integer covariate 11

y

integer post-intervention churn (0/1)

revenues

double post-intervention cash flows ("m" in the "Managing Churn to Maximize Profits" manuscript)
